WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:16.667 --> 00:00:26.633
Immediately after the earthquake,
Odaka district, Minamisoma, Fukushima
View of impending tsunami taken from inside car 
(Viewer supplied footage)

00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:50.500
Escapes tsunami, resumes recording from higher ground

00:01:25.666 --> 00:01:30.666
Tsunami approaches dangerously close to road

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:49.766
Tsunami surges toward road

00:02:34.666 --> 00:02:39.666
Road becomes completely submerged
Waves reach right below higher ground

00:02:50.366 --> 00:03:01.900
Tsunami gradually starts to withdraw

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:33.833
Here comes a second wave.

00:04:50.333 --> 00:05:01.866
With the shoreline erased,
it's impossible to distinguish between land and sea

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:43.133
Descent from higher ground to road below
to resume filming after tsunami recedes

00:06:32.433 --> 00:06:39.533
View of higher ground from where video was recorded

